Danish crime thriller. Sarah and Jan are convinced that there is a link between Nanna's murder and an unsolved case from the past. They must race against time to nail the evidence.


Plot

Sarah Lund is looking forward to her last day as a detective with the Copenhagen Police department. Local politician Troels Hartmann is in the middle of a hard election campaign to become the new mayor of Copenhagen when suddenly, evidence links him to the murderer. But is he really the murderer? At the same time, the girl's family and friends struggle to cope with their loss.
